snippet.title: The game Doggy for Oric 1 / Atmos
snippet.description:
http://hirudov.com presents Doggy for Oric Atmos. This game was developed by Eric Chahi, who later created the cult game Another World.
The decent scroll, nice music and addictive gameplay makes it one of the best games for the Oric computer.
